  "names": [
    {
      "full_name": "Public Joint-Stock Company “Chelyabinsk Forge and Press Plant”",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "PJSC “Chelyabinsk Forge and Press Plant” (PJSC CHKPZ) is one of Russia’s leading enterprises in the machine-building and forging industries. PJSC CHKPZ’s activities are in economic sectors providing a substantial source of revenue to the Russian Federation. In 2012, PJSC CHKPZ entered the Association of Enterprises of the Military-Industrial Complex of the Chelyabinsk Region. Under the state defence order, the company produces shells for artillery ammunition intended for use in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine. PJSC CHKPZ is therefore supporting, materially and financially, and benefitting from the Government of the Russian Federation, which is responsible for the annexation of Crimea and the destabilisation of Ukraine.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}